Introduction
------------

PTX MySQL Export

PTX MySQL Export is a small PHP tool to export MySQL database, store it into
a file (possible to archive it first) and send it via FTP every where.

Code is written in object PHP.

Documentation and Examples
--------------------------
Only what you must set up properly is following:

$params = array(
    'database' => array(
        'db_host'       => 'localhost', 
        'db_name'       => 'db_name',
        'db_user'       => 'root',
        'db_password'   => '',
        'db_charset'    => 'utf8'),
    'ftp' => array(
        'ftp_server'    => '',
        'ftp_username'  => '',
        'ftp_password'  => '',
        'ftp_folder'    => ''
    ),
    'export' => array(
        'export_folder' => './backups/',
        'export_zip'    => 'bzip2',
    )
);